description:
&lt;p&gt;COME AND JOIN OUR TEAM!&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for enthusiastic and motivated Operating Department Practitioners who are patient focused and strive to deliver high quality and safe patient care. You should be committed to working effectively within multi-professional teams and have excellent communication skills . A desire to join a team to develop and implement innovative practice within the theatre complex is essential.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are a friendly and welcoming unit and will support you in your new role. We provide a comprehensive induction package.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;As a place to live, work and enjoy life, Southend on Sea has a lot to offer. The border touches sea, city and countryside with some of England’s prettiest villages and liveliest towns. It is also just under an hour from London making it an ideal base to explore the capital city. We also benefit from being close to Southend Airport which is developing all the time and regularly flies to many European cities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hours: the need to be flexible is essential. The shift patterns include late shifts, weekend and an on call commitment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
